thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Louisa

author: Louisa
title: Louisa
text: Collected from Queenstown, NZ town and returned to Queenstown, NZ airport. Car booking, collecting, return and airport transfer was efficient and friendly. Car was in good condition and drove well. Refuelling garage was Very close to return office. No surprise bills after return unlike some con rental firms I have used previously.
